    "We have renamed this group as sentiment analysis.",
    "The terms generated for Topic 7 consist of words like \"review\", \"product\", \"rating\", and \"comment\" which are common data sources for sentiment analysis applications.",
    "Similarly, there were terms like \"emotion\" and \"opinion\" which indicate emotion analysis and opinion analysis respectively.",
    "Both emotion analysis and opinion analysis are themes used interchangeably for sentiment analysis.",
    "Lastly, terms like \"safety\", \"food\", \" hotel\", and \"drug\" are popular domains where consumer comments, reviews, and ratings are being crawled for sentiment analysis in the literature."
